            <p ana="start" loc="novel1_letter4_chapter16_p469"/>For myself, <seg xml:id="C23_app862-fThomas_end"/>I <seg xml:id="C23_app864-fThomas_start"/>was passive in all <seg xml:id="C23_app864-fThomas_end"/>
